modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds Working Stove, Working Oven, Working Sink, and Working Granite Sink that can be crafted at Level 1 of Advanced Engineering.

The Stove and Oven operate like the Campfire but the do not require fuel.

The Sinks fill empty bottles with murky water by right mouse clicking on the sink with the bottle in your hand.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/DelStryker/Delmod/tree/master/Delmod_Kitchen)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11141-del-stryker-a17-modlet-collection/).
